Package org.apache.calcite.rex

Class RexWindowBound

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.rex.RexWindowBound
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    RexWindowBound.RexWindowBoundBounded, RexWindowBound.RexWindowBoundCurrentRow, RexWindowBound.RexWindowBoundUnbounded
    public abstract class RexWindowBound
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstracts "XX PRECEDING/FOLLOWING" and "CURRENT ROW" bounds for windowed aggregates.
